Author: kitterfly
Text: i wish i knew... it's a cycle of trying to limit my meals, getting hungry and letting myself have a snack because I'm going to be logical and healthy and then feeling guilty at my next meal and trying to restrict to make up for the snacks. so much fun!

Author: sunnshine67
Text: gum gum gum gum   I find that I usually snack more because I like the sensation of eating more than being hungry
